# Allowlist: ignore everything by default, then permit only the files meant to be public.
# This guarantees course-provided data/PDFs are never committed, even with `git add -A`.
*

!.gitignore
!ps1_task1.ipynb

# (Everything else stays ignored: *.parquet data, *.pdf, *_backup.ipynb, test.py,
#  task1_predictions.csv, .ipynb_checkpoints/, __pycache__/, etc.)
